'''thunderstorm''' (''plural'' [[thunderstorms]])
# A storm consisting of [[thunder]] and [[lightning]] produced by many [[cumulonimbus]], usually accompanied with [[rain]] or [[hail]]. (The rain or hail might come from a normal [[nimbus]] too.) A more severe thunderstorm can cause [[mesocyclones]].

